    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": " ## ⚠️ Note\n\nA [video tutorial](https://youtu.be/HaiO-UeiKBA) for this workflow guide is available on my [Youtube channel](https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCn8xmUBunez1SsDVRfZDUGA)",
