    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## Google Maps Automatic Email Scraper\n\nThis workflow automatically scrapes emails from businesses on Google Maps based on a list of queries that you provide.",
        "height": 140,
        "width": 480,
        "color": 7
      },
      "id": "d902819a-e5dd-4aa3-9280-fe8f07a087f8",
      "name": "Sticky Note6",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "position": [
        256,
        256
      ],
      "typeVersion": 1
    },
    {
      "parameters": {},
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.manualTrigger",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        1120,
        544
      ],
      "id": "ddfa038d-ba65-48a2-81f8-b050175f8806",
      "name": "When clicking 'Execute workflow'"
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## Summary\n\n1. The **Execute Workflow** automation starts.\n   - Feeds the specific queries for searching Google Maps.\n   - Calls the **Scraper** automation which does the heavy lifting for each query.\n   - Then waits 5 seconds between executions to prevent issues.\n\n2. The **Scraper Workflow** starts.\n   - Searches Google Maps using the passed down query with Google API.\n   - Sets the Place IDs of each business.\n   - Loops for each Place ID getting the business' website from the Google API.\n   - Calls Apollo API to find a decision maker based on the website.\n   - Calls Apollo API to find the person's email.\n   - Calls ScrapeNinja API to scrape the person's Company LinkedIn.\n\n",
        "height": 360,
        "width": 740,
        "color": 4
      },
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        256,
        576
      ],
      "id": "6df020c0-1739-4c2d-bc60-cd27540b1e22",
      "name": "Sticky Note1"
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "url": "=https://maps.googleapis.com/maps/api/place/textsearch/json?query={{ $json.query }}&key=AIzaSyD89hWEvE0cMa3aCj-1PTJpVxJHxX0pG7s",
        "options": {
          "allowUnauthorizedCerts": false
        }
      },
      "id": "b5f47b31-7440-471a-ba36-469c4de2a657",
      "name": "Query Search Google Maps",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.httpRequest",
      "position": [
        1888,
        496
      ],
      "executeOnce": false,
      "typeVersion": 4.2,
      "alwaysOutputData": false
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "jsCode": "// Extract all place_ids from the search results\nconst results = $input.first().json.results || []\n\n// Create an array with each place_id as a separate item\nreturn results.map(place => ({\n  json: { \n    place_id: place.place_id,\n    name: place.name // Keep the name for reference\n  }\n}))"
      },
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.code",
      "typeVersion": 2,
      "position": [
        2128,
        496
      ],
      "id": "7669aded-246b-44fa-a90a-dc53a694c2e2",
      "name": "Place ID"
    },
